{
  "stem": "7337.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was not going to sleep another night in Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were going to do leave that day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he went to the station, and he booked us tickets for us to leave in the afternoon-- in the afternoon for Paris.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's when we left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "An empty shoe box was all that my father allowed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said that everybody must take an empty shoe box and a piece of string.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, what on earth do we want an empty shoe box for?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, you'll see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, the reason for the empty shoe box became clear during the journey, because after we crossed the French border, there was a knock on the compartment.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the-- the French consul stood there, with his diplomatic bag, in which he had my father's money.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he set himself down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he started counting 1, 2, 3, 4, 1, 2, 3, 4, and he kept his quarter and gave us three quarters.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we needed the shoe boxes to put the money into.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we arrived in Paris with five shoe boxes full of money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's the sort of man he was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He organized it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we were each given a little, like a school bag, a little suitcase.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, anything you can get in there, you can take with you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course, you couldn't get anything into it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think I took some miniature motor cars with me-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We left our apartment standing as it is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was obviously-- well, most of the contents must have been stolen, because, I mean, we never went back.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
